<P>The FRAME OF THE GOVERNMENT Of the <HI>Province</HI> of <HI>Penn&s;ylvania</HI> In <HI>America.</HI></P>
<P>Printed, and Sold by <HI>Andrew Sowle</HI> at the Crooked-Billet in <HI>Holloway-Lane</HI> in <HI>Shoreditch,</HI> 1691.</P>
